<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和观音菩萨站在莲花台上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看着下方红孩儿的洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在就去打红孩儿吧！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，悟空。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她举起手中的净瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这净瓶里有很多水——如同一个海洋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不希望我把它倒出来的时候，伤害到任何动物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨快速念了个咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，这里的土地神来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨。”土地神说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能为您做什么吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要把这甘露倒在红孩儿的山周围。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你让所有的动物都远离这座山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，观音菩萨。”土地神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>土地神飞到了地面。悟空向下看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到一些小动物从灌木里飞快地跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿也从树枝上飞了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，老虎、熊和其他动物也向山下跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，所有的动物都没有了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我要把甘露倒出来了。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始倒净瓶里的甘露。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波涛沿着山坡向下滚动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水面升得越来越高，形成了海洋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水面上只露出山顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，下去把那妖怪引出来。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和他打一架，但不要打败他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把他引到我这里。”悟空跳到了山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出金箍棒打下去。轰隆！洞门碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿跑出了洞，非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你砸了我的大门！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对啊！”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要是不放了唐僧，我就打你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！”红孩儿大笑，然后打了一下自己鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>什么都没发生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的三昧真火怎么没用了？”红孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他看到海水包围了他的山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“那是观音菩萨的甘露。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有这甘露在，你就没法用你的三昧真火了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”红孩儿用枪向悟空捅过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当啷！悟空用金箍棒挡住了红孩儿的枪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿哼了一声又打了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挥舞着金箍棒，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>差点儿打飞了红孩儿手里的枪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这两个人一直打。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空假装害怕，跳到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿也追了上去。他们一直飞到天上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿一直用他的枪去捅悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用金箍棒挡了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞快地向观音菩萨飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞到观音菩萨身后藏了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当红孩儿看到观音菩萨的时候，他停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这里做什么，观音菩萨？”他高傲地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨看着红孩儿，一句话都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我问你为什么在这里！”红孩儿大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨还是没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是孙悟空叫你来这里的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿大叫，“你为什么不说话？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨继续看着红孩儿，一句话也不说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿开始生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起枪朝着观音菩萨扔过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨不见了！红孩儿大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我猜她是害怕我。”他看着空的莲花台，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空是个傻瓜！他赢不了我的三昧真火，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就去找观音菩萨帮忙。她又能干什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一举起兵器，她就逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，这莲花台是我的了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿坐在莲花台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莲花台突然变成了很多剑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从四面八方包围了红孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”红孩儿大叫，“我被包围了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>